            "text": "<h3><strong>More Than Just Outdoor Living</strong></h3><p>MINDYES believes every outdoor space is an extension of who you are — with endless possibilities to live, relax, and gather. We embrace reinvention with the philosophy of going beyond simple storage or furniture. To delight our outdoor lovers with not only a clutter-free yard but a life fully enjoyed under the sun.</p><p></p><p></p><h3><strong>Our Story</strong></h3><p>MINDYES was created with a simple idea: outdoor spaces deserve the same attention, comfort, and functionality as the inside of your home.</p><p>From backyard patios to garden corners, from pet-friendly spaces to weekend relaxation zones, we saw an opportunity to rethink how outdoor living products should look, feel, and perform. Instead of bulky, purely functional items, we design and curate products that combine practicality, durability, and modern aesthetics.</p>"
